game.name: Princess back to School
game.description:
Summer vacations are over and the three beautiful princesses Ariel, Elsa and Rapunzel are ready to go to their school again. It is getting difficult for them to wait anymore to meet their school friends. These three girls are very excited while heading back to school, but also seek for your help to grab some awesome school looks. Would you like to offer your fashion advice to these beauties? Join Princesses Back to School and be prepared to make them the most beautiful girls of school!

Start with Ariel by dressing her up with a black and yellow color short frock with a black belt tied above her waist or purple and white outfit with a black belt! Pair it with a blue color jeans or red color short in this HTML5 dressing game! You can also opt for the white and purple color frock with a knot tied in the middle of it or a red color dress with white dots. Complete her look with a doll her in her hand or a red color handbag, and a pair of white and grey sandals! 

Then help Ariel to find a perfect school outfit. Give her a red color top with some dark red color strips or a white t-shirt with purple jacket! Combine her dress with a short dark purple midi with a black knot at its top or a black short with some fridges at the bottom! Complete her look with a mobile phone and a pair of matching black sandals or red long boots! Hurry up ladies! Third princess Rapunzel is also waiting for her turn. Dress her up by following the same process in this cool fashion game!
